SELECT SBQQ__PrintOrder__c, SBQQ__Active__c, SBQQ__Status__c, SBQQ__ConditionsMet__c, SBQQ__AdvancedCondition__c, SBQQ__Locked__c, SBQQ__TemplateContent__c, SBQQ__ParentTerm__c, SBQQ__Body__c FROM SBQQ__QuoteTerm__c
